'''Gessime Ben Youssef Mustapha Yassine''' (born 22 November 2005) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for {{French football updater|Strasbourg}} club [[RC Strasbourg Alsace|Strasbourg]]. Born in France, he represents the [[Morocco national football team|Morocco national team]].

== Club career ==
After playing for [[FC Istres|Istres]] and [[Marignane Gignac Côte Bleue FC|Marignane GCB]], Yassine signed for [[Ligue 2]] club [[USL Dunkerque|Dunkerque]] in January 2024.<ref>{{Cite web |date=6 March 2024 |title=Football - Ligue 2 : l'Avignonnais Gessime Yassine nommé pépite du mois |url=https://www.laprovence.com/article/sports/2503953275291115/football-ligue-2-lavignonnais-gessime-yassine-nomme-pepite-du-mois |access-date=8 June 2024 |website=La Provence |language=Fr}}</ref> He quickly established himself in the side's starting eleven, and was chosen as Dunkerque's player of the month in February and March. He was elected Ligue 2 young player of the month in February, and was nominated for Ligue 2 young player of the season.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Denis |first=Sebastien |date=7 June 2024 |title=Ligue 2 : l'ascension fulgurante de la pépite marocaine Gessime Yassine |url=https://www.footmercato.net/a7903479115085159513-ligue-2-lascension-fulgurante-de-la-pepite-marocaine-gessime-yassine |access-date=8 June 2024 |website={{Interlanguage link|Foot Mercato|lt=Foot Mercato|fr|Foot Mercato}} |language=Fr}}</ref>

On 17 January 2026, Yassine signed a four-and-a-half-year contract with [[RC Strasbourg Alsace|Strasbourg]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=RC Strasbourg Alsace|url=https://www.rcstrasbourgalsace.fr/gessime-yassine-au-racing/|title=Gessime Yassine au Racing|trans-title=Gessime Yassine at Racing|date=17 January 2026|access-date=19 January 2026|language=fr}}</ref>

== International career ==
In March 2024, Yassine received his first call-up to the [[Morocco national under-20 football team|Morocco U20s]] for two [[Exhibition game#Association football|friendly]] matches against [[DR Congo national under-20 football team|DR Congo]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |last=Alaoui |first=Yassine |date=22 March 2024 |title=Maroc U20: première sélection pour Gessime Yassine |url=https://fr.hespress.com/368960-maroc-u20-premiere-selection-pour-gessime-yassine.html |access-date=8 June 2024 |website=Hespress |language=Fr}}</ref>

== Personal life ==
Born in France, Yassine is of Moroccan descent.<ref name=":0" />

